</div>
<p>
<em>Next, we'd like to learn your views about what would happen both if the U.S. were to keep its troops in Iraq and if the U.S. were to remove its troops from Iraq. First,</em>
</p>
<p>Q.25-26 ROTATED</p>
<p>25. 
<em>If the United States</em> removes all of its troops from Iraq 
<em>by the middle of next year, do you think each of the following would -- or would not -- happen? How about -- [RANDOM ORDER]?</em></p>
<div align="center">
<table class="MsoNormalTable" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td valign="bottom">
<p>
<strong>
<em>2007 May 4-6</em>
</strong>
</p>
